data.description: Great Opportunity to own this 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Brick Richmond Home! Great Room features volume ceilings with Gas Fireplace, Open concept to Dining area with Amazing Kitchen. Kitchen has plenty of cabinets, great area for entertaining, All Appliance to stay. First Floor Laundry & Half bath off Kitchen. Master En-suite with WIC. Full Finished Basement for adding living space, also includes 2 separate rooms and tons of storage and Pool Table. Sump Pump with Back up. Whole House Generator. 3 Car Garage. Huge Backyard with Brick porch and NEW Vinyl Privacy Fence.
